nodes.text: Delquis was a Human male who served as a member of the Corellian Council. During the Galactic War, Delquis planned on saving Corellia if he and the members of the council would serve the reconstituted Sith Empire. In 3640 BBY, he was present when the Barsen'thor was searching for the First Son. He was brutally killed by Councilor Saiak, who was revealed to be a Child of the Emperor.
